        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Don’t let my enemies gloat, saying, “We have defeated him!” Don’t let them rejoice at my downfall. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
